
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "AboutUs";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/General_Layout.cshtml";
}

<div class="container-fluid">

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-12"
             style="width: 100%; padding: 0px;margin-top:30px; background-image: url('/Content/images/about3.jpg'); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; min-height: 330px;">
            <div class="col-sm-12" style="background: rgba(2,2,2,0.4); min-height: 350px;min-width:100% ">
                <br><br><br>
                <h3 class="display-3 animated slideInDown text-center" style="text-shadow:2px 5px 2px maroon;padding-top:60px; color:white;">About US</h3>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row " style="margin:15px; background:#ffecf5; padding-top:20px;padding-bottom:20px;">
        <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
        <div class="col-sm-5 col-xs-6 animated wow zoomIn" style="width:100%; background-image:url('/Content/images/san2.jpeg');background-repeat:no-repeat;background-size:cover;height:400px;">
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-5  col-xs-6 " style="padding-left:25px;">
            <h2 style="color:#000000; font-family:Script MT;">We Plan & Design Wedding</h2>
            <p style="text-align:justify;padding:0px 0px 0px 0px;">
                Under the leadership of Mr. Rahul Kumar, a world renowned award-winning wedding planner, international speaker and trainer, Vivaah Celebrations provides comprehensive wedding planning and management services to couples from all over the world. Having successfully plann+ed, managed and conceptualized weddings in over 23 countries, our team of creative wedding planners are constantly raising the bar in order to deliver the finest and most memorable wedding celebrations worldwide.

                Positioned as one of the finest destination wedding planning company in UAE, Vivaah Celebrations operates globally for Destination Weddings. Whether you’re looking for Indian wedding planners in Dubai or destination wedding planning, Vivaah Celebrations has planned, conceptualized, and managed weddings for some of the most prestigious families in different parts of the world. Offering bespoke solutions for every aspect of wedding planning, our services include everything from initial planning to event operations and wrap up of events.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
    </div></br>
    <div class="row" style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:20px;">
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 animated fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
            <div class="card box-shadow">
                <img class="card-img-top" src="~/Content/images/g1.jpg" width="100%" height="280px" class="img-responsive" alt="Card image" />
                <div class="card-body" style="padding:5px;">
                    <h2 class="card-title text-center" style="color: saddlebrown; font-weight:bold;font-family: Vladimir Script;">Our History</h2>
                    <p align="center" class="card-text" style="font-family:System;">
                        Couples are getting married later in life, so it's not abnormal to settle down in your late 30s or 40s. The upside to this if you know what you want by this age and you've likely had a few different relationships.
                    </p>


                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 animated fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
            <div class="card box-shadow">
                <img class="card-img-top" src="~/Content/images/g34.jpg" width="100%" class="img-responsive" alt="Card image" />
                <div class="card-body" style="padding:5px;">
                    <h2 class="card-title text-center" style="color: saddlebrown; font-weight: bold; font-family: Vladimir Script;">Our Mission</h2>
                    <p align="center" class="card-text" style="font-family:System;">
                        The minimum underage marriage age, when all mitigating circumstances are taken into account, commonly ranges from 15 to 17. Nine states do not allow a person over 21 to marry an underage person.

                    </p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 animated fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
            <div class="card box-shadow">
                <img class="card-img-top" src="~/Content/images/dance.jpg" width="100%" height="280px" class="img-responsive" alt="Card image" />
                <div class="card-body" style="padding:5px;">
                    <h2 class="card-title text-center" style="color: saddlebrown; font-weight: bold; font-family: Vladimir Script;">Our Vision</h2>
                    <p align="center" class="card-text" style="font-family:System;">
                        Finalise your location and budget: The most important thing one needs to work out at the start of all the wedding preparations is to decide a budget and location for the entire festivities.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


    </div>
</div>

